          <![CDATA[ <p><b>2021 ESOP Fairness Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows certain over-the-counter securities to be treated as publicly traded employer securities for purposes of the diversification requirements for employee stock ownership plans (ESOPs).</p>]]>
